snippet.title: Cryptid Farm: Anniversary Update
snippet.description:
You can play Cryptid Farm here!: https://fistflame.itch.io/cryptid-farm
The anniversary update is the most definitive version of cryptid farm yet, with new animations, better synchronization, new upgrades, dynamic cam and added server options!

This marks a full year of on and off development for Cryptid Farm. Thank you all for your support and for playing the game! More updates to come!

Trailer music by Leo at:
https://soundcloud.com/pompadoormat
https://soundcloud.com/meowitzer
(myspace link??)
https://myspace.com/pompadoor.mat?fbclid=IwAR0hoV-jI2-JjjhMDRPp3O6OibMJgXcHX4LeZMXcN7ZeXm4N7UKvB56_MWA

More of my social media:
https://www.instagram.com/topeart/

Full list of changes can be found here:
https://fistflame.itch.io/cryptid-farm/devlog/217889/anniversary-update
